Modifications in this project:
  - Replaced PyTorch inference with ONNX Runtime + numpy
  - Replaced torchaudio mel extraction with librosa
  - Replaced torch.fft ISTFT with real-valued DFT basis matrix (RealISTFT)
  - Removed Whisper dependency (user provides transcript directly)
  - Added pre-computed prompt save/load (.npz format)
  - Added Linkwitz-Riley crossover merge in numpy
